title: [Gleyminn Anni River, Shore]
description: Thick black moss carpets the ground between massive banyan trees, vines hanging low along the shoreline.  Weaving between the flora, a firefly blinks in synchrony with the sounds of the river's arduously slow current gently breaking around a fallen tree.  A stained wooden sign smeared with ichor leans towards the remains of a moss-covered sunken fishing dock beyond the banyans.
